{"type":"message","id":"b6d12faf","parentId":"90513767","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:19:36.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📖 **Word of the Day**\n\n**Numinous** *(adjective)* — Having a strong spiritual or religious quality; inspiring awe, reverence, or a sense of the transcendent.\n\n*Example: Standing alone on the mountain peak at dawn, surrounded by clouds, she felt something numinous — a quiet, overwhelming sense of something far greater than herself."}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775024376232}}
