{"type":"message","id":"a9751e81","parentId":"3353093f","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:30:41.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"☀️ Good Morning, Nrexya! ☀️\n\nHappy Thursday! April 2nd — hope everyone's week is going well. Here's some good vibes to start your day 🖤\n\n✨ **Good News Roundup**\n\n🦏 **Rhinos Return to Uganda!** Rhinos have been successfully reintroduced to a protected area where they'd been extinct since 1983. Conservation win!\n\n⚡ **Solar & Wind Hit Record 17%** of US electricity in 2025 — up from less than 1% in 2005. Meanwhile, Pakistan is seeing a people-led solar boom. Clean energy is unstoppable.\n\n🇰🇷 **A Small Korean Town Welcomed Its First Baby in 17 Years!** A hopeful sign amid the country's ongoing birth rate challenges. One tiny human, one huge celebration.\n\n🤰 **Endometriosis Film Won a BAFTA!** \"This Is Endometriosis\" took Best British Short Film, finally shining a spotlight on a condition affecting millions. Awareness matters.\n\n---\n\n🧩 **Brain Teaser of the Day:**\n\n*I have cities, but no houses. I have mountains, but no trees. I have water, but no fish. I have roads, but no cars. What am I?*\n\nThink you know? Drop your answer below 👇\n\nHave a great day everyone! 🤍"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775097041699}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d8ab3c1","parentId":"a9751e81","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:30:13.964Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📖 **Word of the Day** — April 2, 2026\n\n**Psithurism** *(noun)*\n/sɪˈθjʊərɪzəm/\n\nThe soft, whispering sound of wind rustling through leaves and trees.\n\n> _\"She sat by the window, eyes closed, letting the gentle psithurism of the maple tree fill the silence.\"_\n\nA beautiful reminder that nature has its own language — you just have to listen 🍃✨"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775104213964}}
